Text: When i saw this , i was going WMG but it went to WTF . I already downloaded stuff from this downloader but this one its messed up . From the 11 songs track list are in 4 files . The first file it's just static noise and the other files have sound dips going up and down in volume . I would prefer to have this seeded properly instead of some graphic pictures .
Use a media player that supports cue files.  And no static or dips in audio here.

I tried several things before i posted . BS Player VLC , external DAC , OPPO DAC and the receiver internal DAC . For the first file nothing worked and the dips were and only noticeable at higher volumes on the OPPO . I wish i could get my hands on this in Vinyl but the ones who have it don't sell .
Awesome. Thanks for this in vinyl.
